com.github.cjwizard

Interface PageFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    APageFactory

    public interface PageFactory
    This inteface must be implemented by classes that provide pages for the Wizard.
    Version:
    20140929
    Author:
    rcreswick

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      WizardPage createPage(List<WizardPage> path, WizardSettings settings)
      Creates (or retrieves) a wizard page based on the path of pages covered so far between now and the start of the dialog, and the map of settings.
      boolean isTransient(List<WizardPage> path, WizardSettings settings)
      Check if we must call to createPage(List, WizardSettings) to get the next page or if we can use a cached version.

    • Method Detail

      • createPage

        WizardPage createPage(List<WizardPage> path,
                      WizardSettings settings)
        Creates (or retrieves) a wizard page based on the path of pages covered so far between now and the start of the dialog, and the map of settings.
        Parameters:
        path - The list of all WizardPages seen so far.
        settings - The Map of settings collected.
        Returns:
        The next WizardPage.

      • isTransient

        boolean isTransient(List<WizardPage> path,
                    WizardSettings settings)
        Check if we must call to createPage(List, WizardSettings) to get the next page or if we can use a cached version.
        Parameters:
        path - The list of all WizardPages seen so far.
        settings - The Map of settings collected.
        Returns:
        true if is needed to call to createPage to obtain the next page, false in other case.
        Since:
        20140929
